### 🐛 Describe the bug

torch compile not work when use selective activation checkpoint. Profile results indicate that selective activation checkpoint causes torch compile to not take effect and will not generate triton kernels. The bug is related to https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/144787#issuecomment-3222407495.

```python
